---
title: Smokey Chicken, Bacon & Garlic Crouton Salad with Caramelised Onion & Avocado
description: Tender, smokey chicken pairs perfectly with crunchy bacon & garlic croutons in this hearty salad, brought to life with sweet
caramelised onions. Finished with a creamy mayo drizzle, every bite offers a satisfying balance of smokey, sweet and savoury flavours.
